column6: The next evolution of the Hulk starts here! Bruce Banner's self-imposed exile has come to an abrupt end thanks to one Nick Fury, director of S.H.I.E.L.D. -- and that can only mean a world of trouble! Their meeting sets off a chain reaction of dire consequences for all of humanity, launching the Hulk into outer space and setting the stage for huge happenings in the life of the Jade Giant!
